|   id    |  namespace_id  |   name    |  primary_key_id  |
+---------+----------------+-----------+------------------+
|  16387  |     16385      |  summary  |       none       |
+---------+----------------+-----------+------------------+

admin 'DROP VIEW vw::summary'
replicate
